OL,5, All Sam Rushby can remember about his  
OL,6, family are fleeting memories of        
OL,7, hospital corridors and waiting rooms.  
OL,9,FIn 1994, at just two years old, he lost
OL,10,Fhis mum to Aids. His dad died with the 
OL,11,Fcondition a year later at Liverpool    
OL,12,FRoyal Infirmary.                       
OL,14,FHis sister had also been infected with 
OL,15,FHIV, then a new and untreatable virus, 
OL,16,Fand had died.                          
OL,18,F"My family was literally torn apart and
OL,19,Fripped away from me," he tells BBC     
OL,20,FPanorama in his first-ever interview.  
